choices.text:
### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
### Assistant:

Here is a sample meal plan that meets your dietary restrictions:

Breakfast: Oatmeal with fresh fruit and a tablespoon of flaxseed oil. 
Lunch: Grilled chicken breast with roasted vegetables (such as sweet potatoes, carrots, and broccoli) and a side salad with avocado dressing. 
Dinner: Baked salmon with steamed asparagus and brown rice. 
Snacks: Apple slices with almond butter or a handful of raw almonds. 
Remember to stay hydrated by drinking plenty of water throughout the day. Enjoy your healthy meals!
